AVAILABILITY, CONTENT, SCOPE AND USEFULNESS OF WHAT IS CURRENTLY
AVAILABLE.  IT WILL INCLUDE AN EXAMINATION OF USER GROUPS, BOTH AS
PERCEIVED AND IN REALITY.  MORE SPECIFICALLY, I SHALL CARRY OUT A BRIEF
EXAMINATION OF THE HISTORY OF THE DEVELOPMENT OF NEWS DATABASES,
STARTING WITH THE NEW YORK TIMES INFORMATION BANK AND ENDING WITH THE MOST
RECENT DEVELOPMENTS AT REUTERS. NEWS, NEWSPAPERS, NEWS DATABASES, REUTERS,
NEXIS, TEXTLINE, NEW YORK TIMES INFORMATION BANK, FINTEL, DATASOLVE,
WORLD REPORTER. 
